    "content_id":  "8cc035a1-f6a3-4190-b957-bb291dbbb242",
    "description":  "Find out about MCA CERSANs and their role in enabling CERS users to provide accurate vessel traffic monitoring information on vessels arriving at UK ports.",
    "details":  {
                    "attachments":  [

                                    ],
                    "body":  "\u003cdiv class=\"govspeak\"\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"overview\"\u003eOverview\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis guidance tells you about Consolidated European Reporting System Advice Notes (CERSANS). These have been introduced by the MCA to assist CERS users with providing accurate and timely information to CERS on vessels arriving at UK ports.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"when-will-a-cersan-be-published\"\u003eWhen will a CERSAN be published?\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eA CERSAN will be published when there is a need to:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eProvide detailed guidance on producing information for CERS (i.e. generating CSV files).\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eAdvise of forthcoming procedural or system changes (i.e. new versions of the CERS Workbook).\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eUpdate users on system functionality (i.e. known system issues).\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eRemind users of their reporting obligations when appropriate.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eCERSANs will be targeted at Port authorities, Shipping Agents, Masters calling at UK ports and when appropriate all users.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"where-will-cersans-be-published\"\u003eWhere will CERSANs be published?\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe current list of active CERSANs is available \u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/consolidated-european-reporting-system-advice-notes-cersans\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003ehere\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eA list of withdrawn CERSANs can be found \u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/withdrawn-consolidated-european-reporting-system-advice-notes\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003ehere\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"distribution-of-cersans\"\u003eDistribution of CERSANs\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eTo be included on the distribution list for CERSANs please contact the MCA Maritime Surveillance Team \u003ca href=\"mailto:cers3@mcga.gov.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003ecers3@mcga.gov.uk\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"further-guidance\"\u003eFurther guidance\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eDetailed guidance on vessel reporting requirements is available \u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/how-to-provide-mandatory-vessel-reporting-information-to-the-mca\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003ehere\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e",
